name: J Reno - Lost In The Dark ( CD / Poster )
description:
J Reno is back after 3 years with the highly anticipated new album Lost In The Dark! His most potent work yet, the album features hard hitting production from Anno Domini & Rock It Pro and boasts features from Multi Platinum artists Bizzy Bone of Bone Thugs & Harmony and Bizarre of D12. Other notable features include Psych Ward, So Sick Social Club, Academy & More! 

Hard copies for this album will be a rare item! There will not be alot of these in circulation so book your copy in advance today!

FIRST 50 ORDERS COME WITH A 12x18 POSTER!
